Tallies

21 August 2022

This page provides the most recent tallies of Oryxs excellent list of Russian and Ukrainian equipment losses from the 2022 Russian Invasion of Ukraine1. Up-to-date output datasets can be found at in the oryx_data repo. This repo is updated automatically daily at 22:30 EDT/EST. The code for this tool can be downloaded at scrape_oryx
